### Apply Leave (employee)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Casual",
  "startDate": "2026-03-29",
  "endDate": "2026-03-30",
  "reason": "Personal work"
}

### Get My Leaves
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/my

### Get Leave Balance
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/balance

### Get Pending Leaves (admin/manager)
GET http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/pending

### Approve Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reject Leave (admin/manager)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient balance"
}

### Holidays list
GET http://localhost:3005/api/holidays

### Create Holiday (admin)
POST http://localhost:3005/api/holidays
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Holi",
  "date": "2026-03-30",
  "type": "public",
  "description": "Festival of colors"
}
